== Japanese ==
{{ja-kanjitab|[[停]]}}
=== Etymology ===
English [[bus]] + Japanese [[停留する|停留]](ていりゅう, ''teiryū'') (holding) + Japanese [[所]] [[position]] and this is an abbreviation for it.
